      "bookmarkId": "919891_5_3952-3982",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "3952-3982",
      "markText": "宁捉襟肘以露贫，不借裘马以彰富。有则还吾故有，无则安其本无。",
      "totalCount": 432,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=3952&rangeEnd=3982",
