    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_9_2481-2511",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "2481-2511",
      "markText": "乐不在外而在心。心以为乐，则是境皆乐；心以为苦，则无境不苦。",
      "totalCount": 340,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2481&rangeEnd=2511",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=2481&rangeEnd=2511"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_5_554-592",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "554-592",
      "markText": "武士之戈矛，文人之笔墨，乃治乱均需之物：乱则以之削平反侧，治则以之点缀太平。",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=554&rangeEnd=592",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=554&rangeEnd=592"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_4_574-590",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "574-590",
      "markText": "凡事之不近人情者，鲜不为大奸慝。",
      "totalCount": 288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=574&rangeEnd=590",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=574&rangeEnd=590"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_6_5214-5254",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "5214-5254",
      "markText": "陆之蕈，水之莼，皆清虚妙物也。予尝以二物作羹，和以蟹之黄，鱼之肋，名曰“四美羹”",
      "totalCount": 210,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5214&rangeEnd=5254",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=5214&rangeEnd=5254"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_6_1061-1109",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "1061-1109",
      "markText": "声音之道，丝不如竹，竹不如肉，为其渐近自然。吾谓饮食之道，脍不如肉，肉不如蔬，亦以其渐近自然也。",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1061&rangeEnd=1109",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=1061&rangeEnd=1109"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_6_2496-2543",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2496-2543",
      "markText": "论蔬食之美者，曰清，曰洁，曰芳馥，曰松脆而已矣。不知其至美所在，能居肉食之上者，只在一字之鲜。",
      "totalCount": 204,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2496&rangeEnd=2543",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2496&rangeEnd=2543"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_6_8339-8402",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "8339-8402",
      "markText": "予待三物有差。蒜则永禁弗食；葱虽弗食，然亦听作调和；韭则禁其终而不禁其始，芽之初发，非特不臭，且具清香，是其孩提之心之未变也。",
      "totalCount": 192,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8339&rangeEnd=8402",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8339&rangeEnd=8402"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_3_1342-1372",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1342-1372",
      "markText": "他不仅能从万物的细微处滋养美感，还能在生活的点滴中寻得乐趣。",
      "totalCount": 187,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1342&rangeEnd=1372",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1342&rangeEnd=1372"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_7_4423-4470",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "4423-4470",
      "markText": "我是个贫穷的人，要养活全家五十多口人，虽然有时难免吃不饱，却不会全天挨饿，就是遵循了这个方法。",
      "totalCount": 180,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4423&rangeEnd=4470",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=4423&rangeEnd=4470"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_3_442-482",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "442-482",
      "markText": "“闲情”指的是休闲生活的情趣，“偶寄”则是一种没有任何思想羁绊的散漫式记述方式。",
      "totalCount": 176,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=442&rangeEnd=482",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=442&rangeEnd=482"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_6_8967-9017",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "8967-9017",
      "markText": "然见此物大异葱蒜，生则臭，熟则不臭，是与初见似小人，而卒为君子者等也。虽有微过，亦当恕之，仍食勿禁。",
      "totalCount": 168,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8967&rangeEnd=9017",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=8967&rangeEnd=9017"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_5_2983-2997",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2983-2997",
      "markText": "不佞半世操觚，不攘他人一字。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2983&rangeEnd=2997",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2983&rangeEnd=2997"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_7_3469-3505",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "3469-3505",
      "markText": "饭犹舟出，羹犹水也；舟之在滩，非水不下，与饭之在喉，非汤不下，其势一也。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3469&rangeEnd=3505",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=3469&rangeEnd=3505"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_8_412-488",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "412-488",
      "markText": "“肉食者鄙”，非鄙其食肉，鄙其不善谋也。食肉之人之不善谋者，以肥腻之精液，结而为脂，蔽障胸臆，犹之茅塞其心，使之不复有窍也。此非予之臆说，夫有所验之矣。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=412&rangeEnd=488",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=412&rangeEnd=488"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_5_2301-2335",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2301-2335",
      "markText": "风俗之靡，犹于人心之坏，正俗必先正心。然近日人情喜读闲书，畏听庄论。",
      "totalCount": 156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2301&rangeEnd=2335",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2301&rangeEnd=2335"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_7_581-644",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "581-644",
      "markText": "人则不幸而为精腆所误，多食一物，多受一物之损伤；少静一时，少安一时之淡泊。其疾病之生，死亡之速，皆饮食太繁、嗜欲过度之所致也。",
      "totalCount": 156,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=581&rangeEnd=644",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=581&rangeEnd=644"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "919891_4_823-1137",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "823-1137",
      "markText": "漻漻乎，乎，汶者读之旷，僿者读之通，悲者读之愉，拙者读之巧，愁者读之忭且舞，病者读之霍然兴。",
      "totalCount": 154,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=919891&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=823&rangeEnd=1137",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/94f324b05e095394fc7c2f7?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=823&rangeEnd=1137"
    },
    {
